(31, 'user30@example.com', 123457, 'Logan', 'Hill', 'Wanderlust Adventures', '5556667778', 'Wanderlust Adventures offers unique handcrafted travel accessories and gear that inspire and accompany adventurers on their journeys around the world. We understand the thrill of exploration and the desire to connect with different cultures and environments. Our products are designed to enhance travel experiences while promoting sustainability and supporting local artisans. By choosing Wanderlust Adventures, travelers actively contribute to sustainable tourism and cultural exchange.', '16', 20, 3, 'data:image/jpeg;base64,', 1, 0, 'wanderlust-adventures.jpg');
